frames.caption: A teddy bear dressed in military gear stands in a desolate, war-torn street, embracing a white rabbit plush. The sky is filled with dark, ominous clouds and a flock of birds flying overhead, adding to the somber atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a post-apocalyptic setting with ruined buildings and debris scattered on the ground. The teddy bear and rabbit plush convey a sense of companionship amidst chaos.

frames.caption: A teddy bear wearing camouflage pants and a military-style backpack stands in a desolate urban setting. Birds are flying overhead against a cloudy sky, adding to the somber atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a teddy bear in military attire standing in an abandoned urban area. The environment is bleak, with an old building in the background and birds flying in the sky, suggesting a sense of desolation and solitude.
